{"tid":1790761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大旗嶺新村男子「1926馮氏大屋」內燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T09:07:44.000Z","uid":307683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"709f0f51b15eaa165b432ad0d22f543727156df9","tid":1790761,"uid":307683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"12月20日(五) 14:19<br />\n<br />\n元朗大棠路大旗嶺新村45-46號「1926馮氏大屋」，今晨(20日)10時36分，一名姓周(44歲)男子發現其姓梁(51歲)男僱主倒臥在上址昏迷，身旁有一盤燒過的炭，懷疑他燒炭自殺，於是報警。<br />\n救護員接報趕至，惟經檢驗證實梁男已當場死亡。警方隨即封鎖現場，並未檢獲遺書，經調查後相信事件沒有可疑，不排除事主近日面臨財困。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191220/bkn-20191220141926854-1220_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191220%2Fbkn-20191220141926854-1220_00822_001.html&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Q2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=110212f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191220/bkn-20191220141926854-1220_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9eb6a76f00be4b64f30bdefa265ed21bb4257f01","tid":1790761,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Q2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=2e74f929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Q2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=1bcbd1e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br /